{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce the time of day that fireworks can be set off to between 5pm & 8pm",
        "additional_details": "We think fireworks are a public nuisance and there are endless reports of people setting them off later in the evenings on & around bonfire night in particular. This causes distress & disturbances to many people & animals, resulting in health issues.",
        "background": "Reduce the time in which fireworks can legally be set off to reduce the nuisance & detrimental effect on animals & vulnerable members of the community.",
